Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Kohinoor Square is one of the tallest commercial towers in the country and is an iconic structure located at the centre of the city. Investments in iconic commercial properties appreciate faster and depreciate slower than the market. The building also provides for a conventional ramp parking for your cars and an additional 10 floors of parking. With this, you and your guests will never have to worry about parking.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Large office spaces available in the tallest commercial building in Mumbai.
